text: Bayerotrochus philpoppei is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pleurotomariidae. ==Description== The length of the shell reaches 56 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off the Philippines. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Pleurotomariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2006
title: Bayerotrochus philpoppei
